description:
Dash through the Urban Jungle with a new MX Nitro Expansion: “Blood and Concrete”! Go full throttle through city streets, subways and over rooftops. Take on exciting new Bosses and challenges.
The expansion includes:
- 9 tracks
- 3 Bosses
- 5 achievements
- 3 customization sets
- New soundtrack
- New ranked tracks and more
name: MX Nitro: Blood and Concrete
